{
  "verses": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": [
        "To You I Lift Up My Soul"
      ]
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "To You, O LORD, I lift up my soul;"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "in You, my God, I trust. Do not let me be put to shame; do not let my enemies exult over me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Surely none who wait for You will be put to shame; but those who are faithless without cause will be disgraced."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Show me Your ways, O LORD; teach me Your paths."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Guide me in Your truth and teach me, for You are the God of my salvation;\nall day long I wait for You."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Remember, O LORD, Your compassion and loving devotion, for they are from age to age."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Remember not the sins of my youth, nor my rebellious acts; remember me according to Your loving devotion, because of Your goodness, O LORD."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Good and upright is the LORD; therefore He shows sinners the way."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "9",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "He guides the humble in what is right and teaches them His way."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "10",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "All the LORD’s ways are loving and faithfulto those who keep His covenant and His decrees."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "11",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "For the sake of Your name, O LORD, forgive my iniquity, for it is great."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "12",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Who is the man who fears the LORD? He will instruct him in the path chosen for him."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "13",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "His soul will dwell in prosperity, and his descendants will inherit the land."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "14",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The LORD confides in those who fear Him, and reveals His covenant to them."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "15",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "My eyes are always on the LORD, for He will free my feet from the mesh."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "16",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Turn to me and be gracious, for I am lonely and afflicted."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "17",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The troubles of my heart increase; free me from my distress."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "18",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Consider my affliction and trouble, and take away all my sins."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "19",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Consider my enemies, for they are many, and they hate me with vicious hatred."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "20",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Guard my soul and deliver me; let me not be put to shame,\nfor I take refuge in You."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "21",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "May integrity and uprightness preserve me, because I wait for You.[^57]"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "22",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Redeem Israel, O God, from all its distress."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}